<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">“We will review work styles … with flexibility, ensuring no one has to give up their career due to life events such as childbirth or childcare,” said Tokyo Governor Yuriko Koike. It is unsure how the measure will affect consumer spending of GDP in the country. </span></p>
